description: Use this operation to export results of an Earth Observation job and optionally source images used as input to the EOJ to an Amazon S3 location.

parameters.name: Arn
parameters.description: The input Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Earth Observation job being exported.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: A unique token that guarantees that the call to this API is idempotent. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: ExecutionRoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role that you specified for the job.

parameters.name: OutputConfig
parameters.description: An object containing information about the output file. Path to Amazon S3 storage location for the output configuration file. KmsKeyId (string) --- The Key Management Service key ID for server-side encryption. The URL to the Amazon S3 data input.

nested_params.name: S3Data
nested_params.description: Path to Amazon S3 storage location for the output configuration file.

nested_params.name: KmsKeyId
nested_params.description: The Key Management Service key ID for server-side encryption.

nested_params.name: S3Uri
nested_params.description: The URL to the Amazon S3 data input.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The output Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Earth Observation job being exported.

nested_items.name: ExecutionRoleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role that you specified for the job.

nested_items.name: ExportSourceImages
nested_items.description: The source images provided to the Earth Observation job being exported.

nested_items.name: ExportStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the results of the Earth Observation job being exported.
